title: Colts QB Andrew Luck a full participant at practice
text:
> Indiana Colts QB Andrew Luck a full participant at practice Indianapolis Colts' Andrew Luck watches his teammates warm up before an NFL football game against the Houston Texans, Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015, in Houston. Luck will miss the game with an injury. (AP Photo/Patric Schneider) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team!
